Idaho Territory (1868-07-25)

1868/07/25 -> 1890/07/02

The United States created Wyoming Territory from Dakota, Idaho, and Utah Territories, and from part of ONEIDA.

(Trenholm, 1:83-84; U.S. Stat., vol. 15, ch. 235 [1868], secs. 1, 17/pp. 178, 183; Van Zandt, 136, 144, 156)
